ZH: 这家公司的单位规模很大。
EN: The company has a large scale of operation.

ZH: 一间单位里有10个员工。
EN: There are 10 employees in one unit.

ZH: 我们的单位每年都会举办团建活动。
EN: Our unit organizes team-building activities every year.

ZH: 今天单位开了一次会议。
EN: There was a meeting in the unit today.

ZH: 我们的单位福利待遇很好。
EN: The welfare benefits in our unit are very good.

ZH: 这个单位负责生产这些产品。
EN: This unit is responsible for producing these products.

ZH: 我在这个单位工作已经10年了。
EN: I have been working in this unit for 10 years.

ZH: 他们的单位拥有先进的生产设备。
EN: Their unit has advanced production equipment.

ZH: 新员工入职后会被分配到各个单位进行培训。
EN: New employees will be assigned to different units for training after joining the company.

ZH: 这次活动是由各个单位共同组织的。
EN: This event was organized jointly by various units.

ZH: 他在某个政府单位工作。
EN: He works in a government unit.

ZH: 我们单位近期将要进行搬迁。
EN: Our unit will be relocating soon.

ZH: 他所在的单位需要增加人手。
EN: The unit he works in needs more manpower.

ZH: 这是我们单位的产量报表。
EN: This is the production report of our unit.

ZH: 这个单位提供了很多职业晋升机会。
EN: This unit provides a lot of opportunities for career advancement.

ZH: 他们的单位每月会发布一次绩效报告。
EN: Their unit publishes a performance report every month.

ZH: 我们单位的销售额已经达到了预期目标。
EN: The sales revenue of our unit has reached the expected target.

ZH: 这个单位的办公环境很舒适。
EN: The office environment of this unit is very comfortable.

ZH: 他希望能够调到另一个单位工作。
EN: He hopes to be transferred to another unit for work.

ZH: 我们单位的员工都很团结合作。
EN: The employees in our unit work together in harmony.
